/*------------------------------------------------------------------------
    File        : Ccs.Common.Application
    Purpose     : Provides a well-known point to find references to specific CCS Manager components.
    Author(s)   : pjudge@progress.com
    Created     : 2017-03-13 
    Notes       : 
